BAIL HEARING - 
Defendant in custody and appearing by video from the Manitowoc County Jail.  The State informs the Court that the defendant will be charged with the crime of 2nd degree sexual assault with a person who has not attained age of 16, 2 cts. causing child to view/listen to sexual activity, 2 cts. exposing child to harmful materials.  The matter is continued for initial appearance on 08-15-22 at 1:30 p.m.  Bail is set at $5,000.00 cash bond with the conditions that he report to the Manitowoc City Police Department for fingerprints, photographs and identifying information within 48 hours or, if incarcerated, within 72 hours of release, defendant is to have no contact with E.M.K., DOB: 10-03-2011, defendant is to have no contact with anyone under the age of 18 and defendant is not to possess or use any internet enabled devices.  Bail not furnished and defendant is remanded to the custody of the Sheriff.
